programme for analysts)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The overall goal of the project is to educate business executives, managers and future business professionals how to incorporate best practices of corporate responsibility into their business models. The project builds on the Pontis Foundation&apos;s more than ten years of experience with developing the concept of corporate responsibility in Slovakia, Serbia, Macedonia, and Belarus. In Belarus, we relate and build on our project that aims to develop cross-sectoral partnerships between non-governmental organizations and the business sector. Consequently, the training series for MBA lecturers as a part of the project is as a way of combating this paucity of expertise. ;</narrative>
  </description>
